\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"184e3d3087ad1f529aef826533569723d6259ed2","tid":1207573,"uid":257238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:30:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34710562e57922ee09c75063055948285c9cb394","tid":1207573,"uid":45400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"黎緊 有乾糧 濕紙巾"},{"pid":"dad6d35151ef810215f628f11755faf72556c599","tid":1207573,"uid":12839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"12/6 13:44 From 我認識既物資站工作朋友<br />\n<br />\n真需要物資<br />\n需求高至低排<br />\n廚房紙，紅白藍，退熱貼<br />\n頭盔，索帶，眼罩，口罩<br />\n<br />\n水，食物暫時有海量未消耗得切<br />\n<br />\n勞工手套已有大量，如果買到就買好少少既，但請勿買硬殼果種<br />\n較剪同各種工具請自行衡量危險性<br />\n<br />\n* 最重要係送去中信同龍和道物資站，如果送去大站都係要步兵送過去"},{"pid":"e7d58001fc07685add5054fefec8d1ebd14d4158","tid":1207573,"uid":12839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"剛係現場 需大量頭盔眼罩手套索帶鹽水<br />\n<br />\n海富中心出口大量義工物資站，可比佢地"},{"pid":"6fc2cc8a6e421ff1eed108faeed0b61c6574d75a","tid":1207573,"uid":232523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d58001fc07685add5054fefec8d1ebd14d4158","tid":1207573,"uid":12839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"剛係現場 需大量頭盔眼罩手套索帶鹽水<br />\n<br />\n海富中心出口大量義工物資站，可比佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我收工先黎，如果可以請keep住間中update 吓<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}